# формат7.рф (punycode для корректного выпуска сертификата Let's Encrypt)
xn--7-7sb9ahkoj.xn--p1ai, www.xn--7-7sb9ahkoj.xn--p1ai {
  encode zstd gzip

  handle /api/* {
    reverse_proxy backend:8000 {
      header_up X-Real-IP {remote_host}
      header_up X-Forwarded-For {remote_host}
      header_up X-Forwarded-Proto {scheme}
    }
  }
  handle /health {
    reverse_proxy backend:8000
  }

  reverse_proxy frontend:3000 {
    header_up X-Real-IP {remote_host}
    header_up X-Forwarded-For {remote_host}
    header_up X-Forwarded-Proto {scheme}
  }


  log {
    output file /data/access.log {
      roll_size 50MiB
      roll_keep 5
    }
  }
}
